Module dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform
Package dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.registry

Interface DeferredConverterFactory<T>

Type Parameters:
T - resource type
All Known Subinterfaces:
DeferredConverterFactory.ActionStrat, DeferredConverterFactory.AudioStrat, DeferredConverterFactory.RenderableStrat, DeferredConverterFactory.VectorStrat
All Known Implementing Classes:
ActionStratDeferredConverterFactory, AudioStratDeferredConverterFactory, RenderableStratDeferredConverterFactory, VectorStratDeferredConverterFactory
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface
public interface DeferredConverterFactory<T>
Generates converters converting primitive objects to deferreds. Primitive objects include: 
 String
 Number
 Iterable
 Map
Clients can obtain a module-path-loaded instance of a converter factory using get(Class) with the relevant provider type.
